				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				    As for the question of &quot;Maxed Out&quot;, this occurs approximately the level before you get a new set of spells. Thus, if you are level 4 your new spells should max (those that get stronger with time) at level 7.<BR>
<BR>
